claim.claim-text:
15. A tungsten carbide-based cemented hard material, comprising:
tungsten carbide having an average particle size of 0.1-1.3 μm;
1.0-5.0% by weight of (Co+Ni), with a ratio of Co to (Co+Ni) in % by weight of 0.4≤Co/(Co+Ni)≤0.95;
0.1-1.0% by weight of Cr, with a ratio of Cr to (Co+Ni) in % by weight of 0.05≤Cr/(Co+Ni)≤0.20;
0.01-0.3% by weight of Mo; and
0.02-0.45% by weight of Me, where Me is one or more elements selected from the group consisting of Ta, Nb, Hf and Ti; and
0.01 Me/(Co+Ni)≤0.13.
